---
title: Cheesy Veggie & Bean Enchiladas with Mixed Salad
description: Enchiladas – what could be more fun? Take one part tasty beans and veg, one part soft tortillas, then combine them and top the whole thing with melty cheesy goodness. With a fresh side salad, this is a sure-fire winner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mexican-bean-enchiladas-df9de08d.jpg
